summary: Am I the only one who saw the starters and saw that their silhouettes are extremely similar? If you erase their secondary...
body: Am I the only one who saw the starters and saw that their silhouettes are extremely similar? If you erase their secondary characteristics (ears, tails, etc) their head and torso look the same. Now I don’t hate the starters, not at all, but we’ve had starter trios who looked different from each other in the past so this is just a little disappointing. For all I know the starters could be similar to each other for a reason, so if that’s the case I’ll eat my words.
